Package: dcce
Title: Dynamic Common Correlated Effects Estimation for Panel Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Mustapha", "Wasseja", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "mwasseja@worldbank.org")
Description: Estimates heterogeneous coefficient models for large panels
    with cross-sectional dependence. Implements the Mean Group (MG),
    Common Correlated Effects (CCE), and Dynamic CCE (DCCE) estimators
    of Pesaran (2006) and Chudik and Pesaran (2015), the regularized CCE
    of Juodis (2022), long-run estimators including CS-DL, CS-ARDL, and
    PMG (Chudik et al. 2016; Shin et al. 1999), the CD cross-sectional
    dependence test suite of Pesaran (2021), Juodis and Reese (2022), and
    Fan et al. (2015), and the exponent of cross-sectional dependence
    from Bailey et al. (2016, 2019). Information criteria for CSA
    selection (Margaritella and Westerlund 2023) and the rank condition
    classifier (De Vos et al. 2024) are also included.
